        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer922215248" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9713737440266870509">I LOVE JOSEPH CONRAD. I don&apos;t even know... there&apos;s just something about his writing that makes my brain happy. <br/><br/>I generally hate seafaring stories, but his are so much more than that. There&apos;s so much depth to his writing, and so much insight into the human psyche. Also, I have yet to read an author who does a more convincing oral-narration voice.<br/><br/>Also also... the man didn&apos;t even learn English until he was an adult. How he then managed to write in English with more finesse than 99% of English-speak</span>
  <span id="freeText9713737440266870509" style="display:none">I LOVE JOSEPH CONRAD. I don't even know... there's just something about his writing that makes my brain happy. <br /><br />I generally hate seafaring stories, but his are so much more than that. There's so much depth to his writing, and so much insight into the human psyche. Also, I have yet to read an author who does a more convincing oral-narration voice.<br /><br />Also also... the man didn't even learn English until he was an adult. How he then managed to write in English with more finesse than 99% of English-speaking writers have managed to do before or since STAGGERS me. RESPECT, DUDE. Respect. *bows to Conrad's genius*</span>
  <a data-text-id="9713737440266870509" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

